{"tid":1848514,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"德政！支那免費提供一條龍屍體火化服務","createTime":"2020-01-28T13:25:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T09:08:41.000Z","uid":32511,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"eaba59cc2f11fed090de0ab356f8d9062cce4c24","tid":1848514,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:25:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zcv1YhM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzcv1YhM.jpg&h=ec6e825c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢民政局宣布自1/26起死於武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒）(疑似)的逝者，遺體火化免收費用"},{"pid":"248db849ffc7070e8ce02e9fc5ab5614e0278e96","tid":1848514,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:25:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">除咗醫護之外<br />\n垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">學校停 康文設施都停<br />\n啲人就湧晒去唔停嘅中心<br />\n社區爆發岌岌可危<br />\n<br />\n<ins>要求立即停止所有非緊急服務</ins></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d36489f4c0dec03863a5bd38e6a0cfbc5be13701","tid":1848514,"uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2C1gNbB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2C1gNbB.jpg&h=707c6bd5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jznr9pX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJznr9pX.jpg&h=c3305560&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a4e68bb8458c78399fe608e1345cbe9a86e98a56","tid":1848514,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:27:52.000Z","msg":"噉咪有人為咗唔想畀錢而集體自殺?<img src=\"/assets/face